{"title":"Faserwerk Baslerstab bolts carbon MTB bar straight to your steerer, no stem needed!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/30/faserwerk-baslerstab-bolts-carbon-mtb-bar-straight-to-your-steerer-no-stem-needed/","date":1630332035000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div data-off-canvas-content=\"\"><main role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-269789\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><header></header><section itemprop=\"text\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100516/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_on-bike.jpg\"><figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100516/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_on-bike.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs%3Adevice%2Frscb28-1\" alt=\"Faserwerk Baslerstab direct-mount lightweight carbon MTB handlebar, on bike\" loading=\"eager\" data-feature=\"1\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\"></figure></a><p>Out of the component R&amp;D lab of ARC8 bikes come this wild new carbon Faserwerk Baslerstab mountain bike handlebar. The Baslerstab takes integrated one-piece cockpits to the extreme. No stem needed, the bar literally bolts straight to the steerer tube of your fork with its own rear-facing faceplate.</p><h2>Faserwerk Baslerstab direct-mount lightweight carbon MTB handlebar</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:740x101/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"Faserwerk Baslerstab direct-mount lightweight carbon MTB handlebar, top\" width=\"2200\" height=\"300\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 2200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-297x41.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-800x109.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-120x16.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-768x105.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-1536x209.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-2048x279.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2200px) 100vw, 2200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:740x101/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.5735543397968337\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 2200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-297x41.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-800x109.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-120x16.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-768x105.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-1536x209.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100508/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_top-2048x279.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 2048w\"></a></p><p>As mountain bikes get more aggressive, longer enduro-inspired geometry, MTB stems keep getting shorter. And with improved ergonomics from more backsweep, Faserwerk was able to bend their new Baslerstab carbon MTB bar so that it sat just in front of your fork’s steerer. Then all they needed to do was shape a recess for the steerer and add a rear face plate to bolt the bar directly to your fork’s steerer tube, without the need for a stem at all.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Faserwerk Baslerstab direct-mount lightweight carbon MTB handlebar, clamp\" width=\"2022\" height=\"1137\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail.jpg 2022w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2022px) 100vw, 2022px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail.jpg 2022w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100512/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_clamp-detail-1536x864.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>The result is a superlight 240g carbon bar that’s still 800mm wide with 35mm &amp; 50mm effective stem lengths available. The Faserwerk Baslerstab bar gets 15mm of rise, 9° of ergo backsweep, and 6° of upsweep.</p><h3>Faserwerk Baslerstab carbon MTB bar – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100505/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_angled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100505/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_angled.jpg\" alt=\"Faserwerk Baslerstab direct-mount lightweight carbon MTB handlebar, angled\" width=\"1800\" height=\"850\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www