oimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100505/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_angled-120x57.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100505/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_angled-768x363.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/30100505/Faserwerk-Baslerstab-direct-mount-lightweight-carbon-MTB-handlebar_angled-1536x725.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>The full carbon Faserwerk Baslerstab bar is made in ARC8/Faserwerk’s own factory. It is available now direct from ARC8 or their dealer bikeshops from today for $299 / 299€ in either 35mm &amp; 50mm virtual stem lengths.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.arc8bicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>ARC8bicycles.com</em></a></p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"cecf64345d560f83ec7620a82ee751edfa9a7b1b74092f8063411451c4e87852","category":"Cycling"}